--- .gitignore


+++ .gitignore
```
# Environment variables
.env
.env.local
.env.*

# Database files
*.db

# Dependencies
venv/
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Logs
*.log

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.tmp

# Coverage reports
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# Build artifacts
dist/
build/
target/
```
